        <item>
            <title>KatClaw 2026.3.6 (Build 340)</title>
            <description><![CDATA[
                <ul>
                    <li>Skills Manager — 3-tab UI: Installed, Browse ClawHub, Custom editor</li>
                    <li>VirusTotal safety badges for community skills (Safe/Suspicious/Blocked)</li>
                    <li>One-click Homebrew install for missing skill dependencies</li>
                    <li>Homebrew detection with install prompt if missing</li>
                    <li>Custom skill editor with save/restore/delete</li>
                    <li>China region auto-detection for Moonshot/Kimi endpoints</li>
                    <li>Improved chevron tap targets in skills list</li>
                    <li>Missing prereq details: bins, env vars, and config keys</li>
                </ul>
            ]]></description>
